findings.title: Potential unauthorized script upgrade
findings.description: The smart contract may allow an unauthorized user to upgrade the script.

findings.title: Centralization Risk
findings.description: Active contract ownership identified which can lead to centralization of power and risks related to rug pull scams.

findings.title: Low Max Wallet
findings.description: Smart contract owner can change max wallet limit. Minimum limit is set to allow the value change within the set parameters.
